&gt;&gt; <br />
b)<a href="http://tom-eclipse-dev.blogspot.com/2007/01/tableviewers-and-nativelooking.html" target="_blank"> http://tom-eclipse-dev.blogspot.com/2007/01/tableviewers-and -nativelooking.html</a><br />
&gt;&gt; <br />
&gt;&gt; <br />
&gt;&gt;&gt; You are best of when checking out the code from the cvs-repository.<br />
