&gt;&gt;&gt; checkboxes into the table directly, why I can't pull them back out<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt; directly.  That just seems odd to me based on the code I have below when<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt; it seems like I should just need to do a one line method call to get the<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt; button based on the position of the array.<br />
