&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Well if you take:<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />
&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />
&gt; a)<a href="http://dev.eclipse.org/viewcvs/index.cgi/org.eclipse.jface.snippets/Eclipse%20JFace%20Snippets/org/eclipse/jface/snippets/viewers/Snippet056BooleanCellEditor.java?view=markup" target="_blank"> http://dev.eclipse.org/viewcvs/index.cgi/org.eclipse.jface.s nippets/Eclipse%20JFace%20Snippets/org/eclipse/jface/snippet s/viewers/Snippet056BooleanCellEditor.java?view=markup</a> <br />
